        "description": {
            "value": "<p>You create a wave of energy that ripples through the earth. Terrestrial creatures in the affected area must attempt a Reflex save to avoid stumbling as the shockwave shakes the ground.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Flat-Footed]{Flat-Footed} until the start of its next turn.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature falls @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Prone]{Prone}.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> As failure, plus the creature takes 1d6 damage.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Heightened (+1)</strong> The area increases by 5 feet (to a 20-foot cone at 2nd level, and so on).</p>"
